{"type": "article", "id": 18863, "title": "鸟笼盆景", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-11T08:51:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021151489QGbTdqIFHrtpvJw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是俄罗斯设计师 Katia Tolstykh 带来的鸟笼，看上去更像是一个悬挂的盆景。鸟笼杆上爬满的绿色的植物，来给小鸟营造一个自然的城堡。它更重要的特征是一个铜质的扬声器，专门用来放大小鸟声音，让住在屋子里的人感受到更多的自然。鸟笼下的底座是用橡木做的，单独当做室内的盆景也很漂亮。<a href=\"http://katiatolstykh.com/Orator\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115146FdbWJQA4mXgfCLKZ.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"315\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66737288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115147bRk0yfjUSqxcwWls.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"315\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66737288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115147kN0dGu4yAxD5S9tZ.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"315\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66737288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211514837ADeFRwvg4iXp9P.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}